Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:23.85,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}見つめるだけでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:28.30,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あなたは言ったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:38.41,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}違う　違うでしょ　意気地なしで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:44.09,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}二人は引き合うしわのように
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:49.34,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}近づくたびごと震える指先
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:54.47,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}運命以上に触れてみたら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:16:00.70,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}譲れない気持ちで歌うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:05.36,songjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I  SING  FOR  YOU…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:14:01.32,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}若能聽到這聲音  就立刻出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:11.36,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}揮去迷惘  前往笑容的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:18.61,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只要能注視著你就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:23.15,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}雖然你這樣說過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:33.61,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不是  不是吧  想要相伴身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:38.80,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}兩人猶如相互牽引的漣漪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:44.14,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}越是接近指尖越發顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:49.23,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如果觸碰到命運之上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:55.32,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無法退讓的心情將會滿溢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:59.51,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我為你而唱…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:23.85,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只要能注視著你就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:28.30,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}雖然你這樣說過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:38.41,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不是  不是吧  只是因為懦弱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:44.09,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}兩人猶如相互牽引的漣漪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:49.34,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}越是接近指尖越發顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:54.47,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如果觸碰到命運之上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:16:00.70,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}為無法退讓的心情而歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:05.36,songcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我為你而唱…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==========歌詞================
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也很在意乃木坂同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊就別管了  大家我會適當地應付過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  快去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  綾瀨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像說想起什麼很重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  演唱會還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這是在幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:15:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴春香我真正的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  所有的評審都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要發表結果了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮冠會在誰的頭上發光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了春香成為偶像的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾…綾瀨君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茅原小姐  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法答應你那樣的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:16:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後做決定的是春香
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那之前  我有些話一定要對春香說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.41,0:17:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕啊  前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快來人把他抓住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕…裕人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓春香遠離我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.89,0:17:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓春香參加這種甄選會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想讓你獲得優勝去當什麼偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然知道這是我的任性  但是我希望你在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.37,0:17:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是別人  而是在我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我也想在裕人身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想離開裕人去別的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:18:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼時候  都想要感覺到有裕人在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣你就無法成為偶像了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  那個…偶像是指什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是春香全部都知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甄選會的幕後  還有之後出道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  裕人也是和我一起聽說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次參加甄選會是因為投錯了文件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不過是形式上的參加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…你沒聽說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都…都到了這份上  再沒有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發佈結果之後春香小姐就是我們的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼發表結果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十五屆未來型偶像甄選會冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃木坂…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.71,0:18:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那波小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人少爺  您平安無事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出這種事你覺得我們會善罷甘休嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃木坂就是為此而在的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個會場以及甄選會的主辦者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有期間和春香有關的商品  CD等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一切的權益一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都由我們乃木坂家買下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用花言巧語哄騙我的春香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了私利私慾而利用她  實在是膽大包天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦  爸爸冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.45,0:19:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然騙了春香是不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但經過調查  這也是為了讓出色的偶像出道才這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說姐姐她有偶像的資質
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為父親也應該很自豪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著這份上原諒她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才裕人的那番話  讓我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪兒都不會去  一直留在裕人身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和預料的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.51,0:20:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人比起經紀人更適合這邊的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:20:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  新曲熱賣的米蘭醬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像最近在徵募經紀人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  條件是不遲到  又有些體力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  可樂放碳酸氣很拿手的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然晚了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.12,0:21:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人節巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  是自彈鋼琴曲的CD
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了巧克力  還想送些什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後前一陣的課程裡有錄音的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就拜託彌生小姐她們做了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你決定參加甄選會的理由是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想著裕人而彈的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能合你的心意就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.36,0:22:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.93,0:22:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕裕裕裕裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.94,0:22:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.59,0:22:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.09,0:22:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大哥哥變得機靈起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為總是會變成這樣呢  真是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.95,0:22:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過居然突然抱住人家  大哥哥還真有一手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.07,0:22:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的越來越大膽了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.17,0:22:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大膽  Come  here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================================
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.25,0:24:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「乃木坂用語的基礎知識」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.22,0:24:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的詞是「purezza」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.24,0:24:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是音樂用語之一  義大利語中「清純」的含義
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.83,0:24:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是和春香很相襯的詞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.47,0:24:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪…哪有  裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.67,0:24:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.70,0:24:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.84,0:24:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.91,0:24:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.14,0:24:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香
